ctu.nengoros.rosparam

Interface PrivateRosparamInt

  • All Superinterfaces:
    NodeInfoInt, RosparamInt
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PrivateRosparam, PrivateRosparamNode

    public interface PrivateRosparamInt
extends RosparamInt
    This is able to simply read private parameters of a ROS node from the parameter tree. This reads private nodes parameters, which can be setup e.g. from commandline during launch, example parameter: _parameterX:=10.4
